Package: vhtcpd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser, lsb-base
Description: HTCP-to-PURGE forwarder for Varnish
 A network daemon that listens for multicast HTCP cache purge requests
 and forwards them to Varnish via the HTTP PURGE method.

